precis:
Enactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON
TERRITORY (1999, No. 1, WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which
(a) prohibits staking mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals
on lands which may be required for the settlement of Aboriginal land
claims, and (b) repeals the Prohibition Order made by Order in Council
P.C. 1996-1846.
